annotations.title: Arbitrary Nature of Time

textContent:
1.5oz 100 Proof Bonded Rye
1oz (30ml) Campari
.5oz (15ml) Cherry Heering
4 drops Mole Bitters
2 dashes Orange Bitters

Stir over ice in glass.
